Company Overview of Horizon Bancorp, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
As of December 31, 1998, Horizon Bancorp, Inc. was acquired by City Holding Co. Previously, Horizon Bancorp, Inc., through its subsidiaries, provided financial and trust services to individuals and commercial customers throughout southeastern and southwestern West Virginia. The bank offered commercial loans, residential real estate loans, and consumer loans. It also offered a range of deposit products, including interest bearing and noninterest bearing demand accounts, savings accounts, and certificates of deposits.


One Park AveBox DBeckley, WV 25802-2803United StatesFounded in 1984419 Employees



Phone: 304-255-7000








