	Online Trust Login





Horizon Bank Online Trust enables you to manage your retirement planning and trust investments through a secure web portal from any internet-enabled device. Using our new online access system, Weblink, you will be able to take control of your financial future.  


		User customization of data displayed on reports

		Ability to display portfolio information on trade date

		Display of long- and short-term gains/losses

		Ability to view pending trade transactions in addition to settled trade transactions

		Ability to hyperlink from ticker symbols to investment information on the Internet

		Cash projection information for up to 99 days 





	Investment vehicles made available through Horizon Trust & Investment Management are: Not deposits or other obligations of, or guaranteed by Horizon Bank; Not insured by the FDIC; Subject to investment risks, including possible loss of principal.






















 

